BEST Kids Makeup Tutorial Unboxing Makeup Kit Unicorn & Mermaid Makeup Brushes Review by Tiffany Taylor Now before everyone gets all worked up YES Tiffany Taylor is only 4…NO…she won’t be wearing this everyday. Yes…she is beautiful the way she is and I tell her that everyday. This make up is JUST FOR FUN, for her DIY LOL Surprise makeovers, for halloween makeup tutorials and kids makeup challenges. I do not like using MY makeup on her so I did some research and found THE BEST REAL SAFE MAKEUP for kids! This makeup beauty kit is perfect for tweens and for girls who are just learning and experimenting with makeup. Let me just say that these makeup brushes are SUPER CUTE! So HAPPY with this makeup and beauty products! Keep reading for full details!
Ammiy Unicorn Makeup Brushes Set Fantasy Makeup Tools With a Cute Iridescent Holographic Carrying Case (Amazon’s Choice) 
These unicorn makeup brushes are cruelty free with nylon hair and handle material plating, plastic. Including 10 different shapes and sizes of brushes. Based on high quality hair, it provides superb ability to hold powder, soft and pleasing for your skin. Best gift for your friends or family members. The handles of the brushes are twisted like a Unicorn Horn in a very pale pearly lilac shade, unique design brush pole shape , to ensure comfortable feel and easy to use. These unicorn brushes Intended for makeup beginner and enthusiasts, the creative possibilities are endless. The unicorn makeup brushes are comfortable to hold with the twisted design on the handles, and very lightweight too. The case they come in helps you to keep them all together and in good condition, and of course, you can take it with you if you're away from home. 
Mermaid Makeup Brush Set Professional Eye Makeup Brushes- Odour free, safe for sensitive skin. Non-shedding, easy to stick powder as well as easy to clean and dry off fast. Popular Mermaid Shape: Bright multi-color gradient premium plastic handles with 3D fish scale will give you an incredible touch feeling and stylish visual feel. Suitable for both professional or individual use. Usage: This mermaid makeup eye brushes are both suitable for applied to liquid, powder or cream cosmetics to produce a flawless eye looks. Ideally for applying, shading and blending products to show your natural beauty. Two gradient color for you to choose. Also the best multipurpose eye brush set to create a perfect smoky eye looks or other eye makeup applications.
SHANY ‘Fix Me Up’ Makeup Kit, Multi by SHANY Cosmetics UNBOXING and REVIEW- This makeup kit is full of vibrant makeup. Grand total of 36 matte or pearl finish eye shadows. Eight lip colors with a semi-glossy finish and applicators. True-to-color and super pigmented makeup that silky soft. SHANY is a member of PETA and products are cruelty free designed by makeup professionals in the U.S.A. This beauty kit is that it is better than any of the “play" makeup I have seen. The colors are very rich and pigmented which is perfect for kids who really want to see the makeup when they look in the mirror. This makeup kit looks more “mature” than play makeup so it is perfect for girls between ages 6 and up (tweens) who wouldn’t want a makeup set for “little kids.” This beauty makeup kit arrived in PERFECT condition and it is packaged well. I also love that it is not long lasting and washes off easily.

Former park manager Claire Dearing creates a dinosaur rescue organization and teams up with Benjamin Lockwood, the former partner of John Hammond, to bring the creatures to a sanctuary in America. Claire's boyfriend Owen Grady, a former dinosaur trainer at the park, joins the mission to locate Blue,[7] the last of the Velociraptors that he trained.  However, a greater scheme emerges when the creatures are being auctioned away, and disaster strikes when a dangerous hybrid dinosaur, the Indoraptor, escapes and begins terrorizing people.

Five Nights At Freddy's Toys for Kids FNAF Toys Unboxing Set Puppet  Toy Review Bonnie Chica funko Toys. These toys are like the funco toys. Jazzy Puppet's FNAF Toys come to life and do Jumpscares in this Five Nights at Freddy's 5 Inch action figure toy review. Five Nights at Freddy's Toys for kids are super fun! The Five Nights at Freddy's toys are supposed to stay on the shelf, but they come to live, eat all of the dogs food, and then run away! Jazzy Puppet screams when the Five Nights at Freddy's Jumpscares happen! They are funny FNAF jumpscares though! Non of the FNAF Jump Scares are not scary. My favorite is the Toy Chica FNAF action figure, and I love FNAF videos! These are similar to FNAF Mcfarlane toys and come from the FNAF world! You will love this family friendly video. snippet.title: Birthday Haul! Nerf Elite and X-Shot Blaster Unboxing and Review
snippet.description:
We're celebrating a birthday on Kids Toys Play, by unboxing some awesome Nerf review and Zuru X-Shot blasters! We've got the Nerf N-Strike Elite Roughcut 2x4 and Zuru X-Shot Flying Bug Attack and 2x Xcess sets, and a ton of darts! We even have the new Thomas and Friends trackmaster push along Birthday Celebration train set! Lots to unbox and review on our family friendly channel for kids!

Zuru X-Shot Flying Bug Attack Double Swarm Seeker 0:15
Take down flying targets with X-Shot Flying Bug Attack! Place your bugs onto the motorized launcher, step on the pedal and release it to see bugs soar in the air. Take them down with the exclusive Swarm-Seeker blaster!

KEY FEATURES:

• Real Flying Bug Attack that hover in the air for you to blast down!

• Motorized launcher that works by pressing its button down with your foot so you have your hands free to shot down the bugs!

• Release the pedal and watch your bugs fly through the air. Take them down before they land!

• The Swarm-Seeker is specially tailored for quick fire with its 10 dart capacity magazine so you\'ll have plenty of shots to hit your targets!

Zuru X-Shot 2x Xcess 1:07
With a pull to prime mechanism and a dual dart system firing both discs and darts, from a special rotating double barrel system, your opponent won’t know what hit them!

KEY FEATURES:

• Shoots darts up to 80ft/24m

• 6 Dart Capacity (each) Dual Barrel

• Discs for short range targets

PACK INCLUDES:

1x X-Shot XCESS Blaster

12x X-Shot Foam Darts

Nerf N-Strike Elite Roughcut 2x4 2:00
Slam into battle with the double-barreled excellence of the ROUGH CUT 2X4 blaster! This sleek blaster lets you launch 2 Elite Darts at once at targets up to 75 feet away, and the pump-action design lets you pump repeatedly to unleash a steady double stream of darts! Launch up to 8 Elite Darts without reloading! As with most N-STRIKE blasters, the Tactical Rail lets you add most N-STRIKE Tactical Rail accessories (sold separately) for more battle capability. Power up the multishot madness of the ROUGH CUT 2X4 blaster and get ready to dominate with both barrels!

KEY FEATURES:

• Real Flying Bug Attack that hover in the air for you to blast down!

• Motorized launcher that works by pressing its button down with your foot so you have your hands free to shot down the bugs!

• Release the pedal and watch your bugs fly through the air. Take them down before they land!

• The Swarm-Seeker is specially tailored for quick fire with its 10 dart capacity magazine so you\'ll have plenty of shots to hit your targets!

Zuru X-Shot 2x Xcess 1:07
With a pull to prime mechanism and a dual dart system firing both discs and darts, from a special rotating double barrel system, your opponent won’t know what hit them!

KEY FEATURES:

• Shoots darts up to 80ft/24m

• 6 Dart Capacity (each) Dual Barrel

• Discs for short range targets

PACK INCLUDES:

1x X-Shot XCESS Blaster

12x X-Shot Foam Darts

Nerf N-Strike Elite Roughcut 2x4 2:00
Slam into battle with the double-barreled excellence of the ROUGH CUT 2X4 blaster! This sleek blaster lets you launch 2 Elite Darts at once at targets up to 75 feet away, and the pump-action design lets you pump repeatedly to unleash a steady double stream of darts! Launch up to 8 Elite Darts without reloading! As with most N-STRIKE blasters, the Tactical Rail lets you add most N-STRIKE Tactical Rail accessories (sold separately) for more battle capability. Power up the multishot madness of the ROUGH CUT 2X4 blaster and get ready to dominate with both barrels!

snippet.title: 2018 ANGRY BIRDS McDONALDS HAPPY MEAL TOYS UNBOXING KIDS COLLECTION EUROPE UK FULL SET 12 PREVIEW
snippet.description:
New next 2018 Angry Birds McDonalds Happy Meal toys Rovio full set of 12 Angry Birds kids meal toys world collection Europe UK unboxing preview. Fast Food Toys previews the new 2018 McDonald's Angry Birds Happy Meal toys and there's a complete set of 12 x 2 = 24 Angry Birds toys. There were also many McDonalds The Angry Birds Movie Happy Meal toys in 2016. They each come with an Angry Bird on the package, 2 birds inside, a green piggy target and 2 plastic / wood planks! Each Angry Bird Happy Meal box comes with a free Zappar app zap code to scan code for some Angry Birds play and also free e-book code voucher coupon! The first 4 Angry Bird toys are: Jim of the Blues, Chuck, Matilda & Stella. Meanwhile Burger King will have the Hotel Transylvania 3 toys. The next McDonald's toys will be either the Grinch movie or the Disney Wreck-It Ralph Breaks The Internet 2 Happy Meal toys after these toys and the Bumblebee movie, My Little Pony toys, Justice League Action, Super Mario & Hasbro Gaming toys. McDonald's Mexico & Brazil and Latin America have the Animal Jam toys after Super Mario. We will do the unboxing of all the McDonalds Angry Birds toys shortly & will review them unboxed! McDonald's UK & Canada have the 2018 McDonalds Angry Birds Happy Meal toys & Hasbro Gaming after the McDonalds Hotel Transylvania 3 & the Amazing World Of Gumball Happy Meal toys.

McDonald's Angry Birds Happy Meal toys are known worldwide. In Brazil they are known as mclanche feliz brinquedos angry birds while in Mexico they are cajita feliz juguetes angry birds.
We love the Rovio Angry Birds McDonalds Happy Meal toys advert. The 3 McDonalds Angry Birds Happy Meal toys boxes are: #1 Red #2 Chuck #3 Bomb.

snippet.title: LEGO Friends Heartlake City Hospital (41394) - Toy Unboxing and Speed Build
snippet.description:
Heartlake City Hospital

Item: 41394
Ages: 6+
Pieces: 380

Kids can learn the value of caring for others while role-playing as a doctor, ambulance driver or patient with this LEGO® Friends Heartlake City Hospital toy playset (41394). It makes the best gift toy for children aged 6+ who will love acting out authentic scenarios in the hospital's reception area, the examination, recovery and storage rooms and its rooftop garden. So many ways to play! Buildable medical equipment, such as the X-ray scanner and microscope, plus bandage, stethoscope, syringe and thermometer accessories inspire imaginative play, as do the 3 mini-doll figures – LEGO Friends character Emma, Ethan and Dr. Maria. Add to the creative play possibilities with the toy ambulance to transport injured Ethan to the hospital, plus a stretcher and a wheelchair. Introducing LEGO Friends… LEGO Friends building sets are the best toys to encourage young kids to explore their interests with the help of the 5 girls from Heartlake City – Stephanie, Mia, Andrea, Emma and Olivia.
- Kids discover the joy of caring for others when role-playing as doctor, patient and visitor Emma, and recreate real-life scenarios with this colorful and detailed LEGO® Friends Heartlake City Hospital (41394) playset.
- The hospital’s examination room, with a buildable X-ray scanner, rooftop garden and medical accessories, plus 3 mini-doll figures – LEGO® Friends character Emma, Ethan and Dr. Maria – will spark children's creativity.
- Kids will love pretending to drive the LEGO® toy ambulance, which has space for a patient and a stretcher in the back. A mini-doll wheelchair and medical accessories add to the imaginative play options.
- There are so many ways to play with this 379-piece LEGO® set, making it a fun toy birthday gift, holiday gift or special surprise for kids aged 6+ to enjoy on their own or to share the fun with their friends.
- The LEGO® hospital measures just over 7” (19cm) high, 8” (22cm) wide and 2” (6cm) deep, so this compact set won't take up much storage space. Kids can also combine it with other LEGO® sets for even more playtime fun.
- No batteries are required with this building set for kids – constructed purely with LEGO® bricks, it is the best toy for powering up children’s free-thinking creativity, so the fun adventures never stop.
- Thinking of buying this doctor toy for someone new to LEGO® models? No problem – it comes with easy-to-follow, step-by-step building instructions. Open the box and away they go!
- Introduce young builders to the world of LEGO® Friends. A warm welcome awaits them in Heartlake City, where kids can explore their interests with their best friends by their side.
- LEGO® building bricks meet the highest industry standards plus our own quality criteria. Kids building this LEGO Friends playset will find the bricks connect strongly and pull apart easily every time.
- LEGO® bricks and pieces are tested in every way imaginable to guarantee that every young builder's LEGO Friends set meets the highest global safety and quality standards.

Welcome to the Official Fireman Sam YouTube Channel. Fireman Sam is everyone's favourite Hero Next Door! Be sure to subscribe to our channel so you can be the first to watch all the great Fireman Sam videos available on YouTube.

Fireman Sam characters!

* Fireman Sam Jones is the "hero next door", Charlie's older brother and Bronwyn's brother-in-law. He lives at 3 Vale Road next to Trevor Evans. 

* Norman Price, is a seven-year-old boy with a love of practical jokes and skateboarding. 

* Dilys Price, runs the village shop. She is a well known gossip, and has great affection for Trevor, the bus driver. Dilys is the mother of mischief-maker Norman Price

* Penny Morris is Fireman Sam’s female co-worker! Penny is often known to go on adventures with the's children – Sarah and James, Norman Price and Mandy Flood. 

* Station Officer Norris Steele, is the chief of Pontypandy Fire Station. As a former army officer, he insists upon a high standard of efficiency in the fire station. 

* Trevor Evans. His job is as the village's bus driver. He is known for his fondness for cricket, his fear of heights, his awkward manner and general bad luck streak.

* Bronwyn Jones, Bronwyn is a Pontypandy citizen who runs the Wholefish Café and is the mother of Sarah and James.
* Charlie Jones, is a fisherman, Bronwyn's husband, Fireman Sam's brother and father of Sarah and James.

* Derek Price, is Norman's cousin, Mr & Mrs Price's son.

* Helen Flood, is the nurse and mother of Mandy Flood.

* Hannah Sparkes, is an eleven-year-old girl and Joe and Lizzie's daughter. She is the only child in Pontypandy to use a wheelchair.

* James & Sarah Jones, are the well-behaved six-year-old twins of Charlie and Bronwyn, niece and nephew of Fireman Sam.

* Joe Sparkes, is the village's mechanic and father of Hannah Sparkes.
